description.text: this message file contains message for t5adrc package

msg.text: DDSCTL comp '$$s' must be programmed with $$sDYNAMIC since DDS comp '$$s' has live signal(s) on it's corresponding $$s port(s).
DDSCTL comp '$$s' cannot be programmed with $$sDYNAMIC since DDS comp '$$s' has no live signal(s) on it's corresponding $$s port(s).
Since DDSCTL comp '$$s' has programming $$sDYNAMIC, DDS comp '$$s' must have all live signal(s) on it's corresponding $$s port(s).
Since DDSCTL comp '$$s' has programming $$sSTATIC, DDS comp '$$s' cannot have any live signal(s) on it's corresponding $$s port(s).
